    "description": "Curilemu is an adventure-horror game that takes place in the mystical landscapes of Chilean Patagonia. You play as a painter stranded on a mysterious island that is plagued by a sickness that is affecting everything alive. Your goal is to uncover the secrets behind the plague and restore the cosmic balance shattered by it.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362780/extras/a2e5406407dc2280487d560f88a18275.poster.avif?t=1729367624\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362780/extras/a2e5406407dc2280487d560f88a18275.webm?t=1729367624\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362780/extras/a2e5406407dc2280487d560f88a18275.mp4?t=1729367624\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362780/extras/4ab0f52aa746efc54a5cdb5a14cacb0b.webp?t=1729367624\" width=616 height=40 /></span><br>Traverse this puzzling island inspired by Chilean folklore and unveil its mysterious past. Explore abandoned ruins, ancient caves, and hidden temples to discover what is actually happening.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362780/extras/b4ed3af1ac2b63b83ac7e461b9cdd3b0.poster.avif?t=1729367624\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362780/extras/b4ed3af1ac2b63b83ac7e461b9cdd3b0.webm?t=1729367624\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362780/extras/b4ed3af1ac2b63b83ac7e461b9cdd3b0.mp4?t=1729367624\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362780/extras/3fb7b69b41fa0675ff38287e3601615f.webp?t=1729367624\" width=616 height=40 /></span><br>Encounter unspeakable beasts, inspired by the works of the masters of horror. Use you magical powers to face them, or run away to avoid colossal dangers.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362780/extras/c7ad7542544bccd7734936acb1d3c6f2.poster.avif?t=1729367624\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362780/extras/c7ad7542544bccd7734936acb1d3c6f2.webm?t=1729367624\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362780/extras/c7ad7542544bccd7734936acb1d3c6f2.mp4?t=1729367624\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
